The paper proposes a novel algorithm for deep generative models, specifically addressing issues in Variational AutoEncoder (VAE) and Generative Adversarial Network (GAN). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper involves adversarial learning, which suggests the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as likely candidates. Finally, the paper also involves stochasticity-free training, which could potentially fall under the sub-category cs.SD (Sound).
